{"tid":1652100,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"打完流感針後眼瞼下垂，睇唔睇醫生好?","createTime":"2019-10-13T14:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T15:35:49.000Z","uid":177206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2a7b6e0f8d9870ba7047a3aba853a09f4c84b244","tid":1652100,"uid":177206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:31:17.000Z","msg":"話說前日打完流感針，大約24個鐘後隻眼好攰，好難睜到好大，成隻眼好乾同痛。好耐之前試過，之前抽過anti-acetycholine receptor 係正常， 好耐之前既IgG, IgM, IgA 都正常<br />\n<br />\n連續幾年打流感針，今年先係咁<br />\n<br />\n如果睇家庭醫生好似無咩用咁，因為都應該開下眼藥水同埋寫referral。睇Aed 又有排等😢<br />\n<br />\n唔知去唔去睇好🤔因爲呢排都忙，唔想請病假去睇醫生"},{"pid":"4eae6b70b90145eb2bf7f3aabb8b1a87345683e1","tid":1652100,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:31:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5ec7715abcc6a3974c1927cbe073b6c0a028d6f","tid":1652100,"uid":73619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:32:49.000Z","msg":"個身體你既，你話睇唔睇醫生好？"},{"pid":"0206cbe9279393fe0df429a33c19ccf7a0faaa28","tid":1652100,"uid":35693,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:33:52.000Z","msg":"你傻撚左？<br />\n仲唔快啲去睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a81da47ed685c1cc9aab61309ad9cef5240ed50","tid":1652100,"uid":61271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:35:49.000Z","msg":"直去急症室啦"},{"pid":"94d85b3689daeacc9c9bdb49f96ce8788cc96253","tid":1652100,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:36:50.000Z","msg":"快啲去睇醫生啦 好擔心你😔"},{"pid":"2a5e38a39ef02ed51121a3aeaad90d060ff2274f","tid":1652100,"uid":177206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0206cbe9279393fe0df429a33c19ccf7a0faaa28","tid":1652100,"uid":35693,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:33:52.000Z","msg":"你傻撚左？<br />\n仲唔快啲去睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:47:35.000Z","msg":"之前都試過，不過唔係打完流感針之後<br />\n唔似過敏反應<br />\n唔似吉巴氏綜合症<br />\n之前抽過auto immune 血又無野<br />\n而家睇野又無重影，睇醫生都係抽下血，無咩野可以幫到我架bo<br />\n就算入院都係打下IVIG,同埋都未必比我打<br />\n睇黎唔知為咩，可能係心理作用搞到好難睜大眼姐"},{"pid":"cdffc63e03ebf8b1d3cad747d237d5f26902c635","tid":1652100,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eae6b70b90145eb2bf7f3aabb8b1a87345683e1","tid":1652100,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:31:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:19:45.000Z","msg":"咪洗。睇到。唔關呢個帖事。"},{"pid":"9be3ba18b0a8c91bcb73fd0e187081300b87c3ef","tid":1652100,"uid":91432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a81da47ed685c1cc9aab61309ad9cef5240ed50","tid":1652100,"uid":61271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:35:49.000Z","msg":"直去急症室啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:20:06.000Z","msg":"咁樣佢都唔去急症室<br />\n我擔心佢生命就真"},{"pid":"6ac62af1c624bb8ebf81cd06899571b468b7bbb7","tid":1652100,"uid":81385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:26:44.000Z","msg":"似係疫苗引起神經發炎<br />\n<br />\n嚴重要入ICU"},{"pid":"e55a46002714a882cebc624218dc643e62d46ae5","tid":1652100,"uid":56624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:32:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔想請病假去睇醫生</span></span><br />\n<br />\n死咗就真係唔洗請假，快啲去急症室啦!"},{"pid":"b738f13a93c068da0864caa62d41fee66e16bf12","tid":1652100,"uid":196829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:34:49.000Z","msg":"立即去急症室<br />\n<br />\n可以會差到 透唔到氣！"},{"pid":"eb400bb3cc14663d79a7e5c074425e1a39115de2","tid":1652100,"uid":196829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a5e38a39ef02ed51121a3aeaad90d060ff2274f","tid":1652100,"uid":177206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0206cbe9279393fe0df429a33c19ccf7a0faaa28","tid":1652100,"uid":35693,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:33:52.000Z","